::Aerotaur::
       He barrel rolls to the side to avoid the oncoming fire and uses the 
momentary distraction to recover ground on Flicker.  He manages to lower his 
voice this time.  "Look Flicker, I'm only going to say this once.  She has a 
baby.  If you want a hostage, take me.  She has someone who needs her.  I 
don't.  I'm expendable."

--part1_134.1d7f9b00.2bb79d81_boundary
